            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-white border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-2 mb-4">평당가격 계산 예시</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold dark:text-white mb-3">예시: 전용면적 84㎡ 아파트, 매매가 10억원</h3>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1.5">
            <p>· 매매가격: 10억원 (1,000,000,000원)</p>
            <p>· 전용면적: 84㎡</p>
            <p>· 전용면적(평 환산): 84 / 3.3058 = 약 25.42평</p>
            <p>· 평당가격 = 매매가격 / 면적(평) = 10억 / 25.42평</p>
